# trusted_from
# ============
# One regex per line for stable sender identities.  Sender addresses are easy
# to forge, so use this only together with a trusted Path/host when possible.
#
# Exact FAQ bot identity:
# ^Trusted FAQ Bot\s*<faq-bot@example\.invalid>$
#
# Bare or angle-bracket form:
# (?:^|<)moderator@example\.invalid(?:>|$)
